title: 22 October 2015 - Statistics released on experience of the public library service and experience ...
text: ( Source : Department of Culture , Arts and Leisure ) The Department of Culture, Arts and Leisure today released figures on experience of the public library service and experience of museums and science centres by adults in 2014/15. ~ Thursday,
